Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是因为构思之后的剧本而过于操劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏和雾岛同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是搞错集合时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同学 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能帮我去看他们一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请容我重新做一次自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是一夏的姐姐 贵月绘美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是雾岛海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感谢你保护了面临险境的一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我代表我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向你献上诚挚的谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏会由我带回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}发自边境行星的求援信号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前往救援的无人飞船却信号中断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 你现在别说是遇难者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可被当成失踪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你明白我们得知这件事后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有多担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}亲戚间都引起大骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我请了带薪假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}租了最新型的飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}飞来找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我这么担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是你呢 轻浮的喝着小酒过着小日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}甚至还交了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道会闹得这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那个 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}听起来不差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被比自己小的男孩子这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感觉挺新鲜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…既然您知道一夏没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就没问题了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已经开始搜寻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但只要报告说我没事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开发等级F
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在不允许与原住民接触的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}边境行星上的失踪者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从联盟那边看来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}必须要立即确认事态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果他们找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得知你现在的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会马上逮捕拘留你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}根据联盟法予以制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没什么办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我才来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 在事情闹大之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和我一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我没办法和海人分开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}绝对不分开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果你执意要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会给海人还有这个星球带来麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…又没做什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是这种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么不理解我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐…请冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好听姐姐说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}该怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 你自己应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起 雾岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}给你看笑话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月…学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷…川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍摄的时间早就…过了…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么没有穿鞋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学…啊 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏同学她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无论如何都得回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那比如先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后再过来之类的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}现在又是在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样很困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那能不能 把我也一起带去宇宙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我什么都肯做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像那样既粗野又顽固的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真的觉得好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们稍稍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}换个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对我的搜索已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不是那种能够轻易逃脱的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}商量也是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}束手无策了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果非要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定会出大事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留下海人 回到宇宙去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我已经什么办法都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你就要放弃和喜欢的人在一起吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就抱着这么轻言放弃的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过用这种程度的心意 和海人交往的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是…我是什么感受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}轻易放弃 丢下喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么回宇宙去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这星球 真是个好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留下这么多自然风貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明和我们的星球完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知怎的却有种熟悉的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏同学也说过同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在这个星球上 有留于自己脑海中的印象的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才来到了这个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个印象啊 在我的记忆之中也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然不能确定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或许那是一夏和我的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}将那个印象编入遗传基因资料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而我们继承了它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么要这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谁知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞不好有埋着祖先的宝藏什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直没在意这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但说不定 一夏她一直纠结于这个印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在寻找一夏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我扫描了这个星球一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是却没有找到与印象相符的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你说了想要一起去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但不能带开发等级F的星球上的居民去宇宙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少要等这个星球拥有能在恒星间移动的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}与我们接触 并加入银河联盟为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}起码要至此 雾岛同学的愿望才能够实现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要到那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以这个星球的标准时间计算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概要耗时几百年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有没有…有没有什么别的办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要联盟法没有被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你 雾岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这么为一夏着想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…我会带一夏回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是为了她好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那孩子居然有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难得特地来接她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反倒觉得当了坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请问是贵月一夏同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜还没回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐也不知道去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 海他们也是在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不会是忘了要拍摄这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在亲亲热热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是不是有点幸运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:10:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“是”什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海他们人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了啊 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月学姐说她要回宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说接她的人已经来了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有各种各样的缘由什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说已经束手无策了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以电影拍摄也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留在这里也是浪费时间 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等啊 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月学姐她真的想去宇宙么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海会怎么样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐就这样走掉 海人被留下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样下去真的好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜你真觉得这样好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么可能会好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我和姐姐谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我让她把我也带去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}却被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我 并没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能和学姐在一起的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啊 被谷川同学骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 让我进行跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(766,664)}jump
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:12:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 放弃的是不是太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原同学也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}事情的原由我已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能不管啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}伤…伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月学姐不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}电影也拍不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我希望贵月学姐能留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里有雾岛同学在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说出你的真心话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐你其实想要怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不想走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想分开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜欢…海人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}即使与宇宙为敌也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就这么办吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么 要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比如去哪里藏起来之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看来你们遇上麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}给的你们一个喜讯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐能留在地球上？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 虽然可能性当然非常小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但并不是零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}该做什么好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 你在寻找某个留于脑海中的印象的地方是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样的话 我们是不是可以认为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个地球上以前也有外星人来过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但…但是 那里不过是我的印象而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐的姐姐也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她脑海里也有和学姐印象中一样的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 她说地球上并没有与那相似的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要在记忆中留下印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是很费功夫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说不定在那个地方 设置了不能以一夏她们的技术发现的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不就没法调查了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}将一夏调查到的资料与地球的地图进行对比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对啊 如果在地图上找到资料里没有的地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那里就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬 你是怎么想到这个的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有人给了我提示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明明说了那么任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你得感谢你那些朋友呢 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没时间了 赶快行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要找到那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后那里有地球人和外星人接触的痕迹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}地球就不是开发等级F的行星了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果能在搜查队到来之前能找到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 印象中的风景限定在日本当中没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 从对那之中的植物的调查情况来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以限定在信州一带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.61,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}（即是长野县 拜托了老师的取景处）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}绝对要找出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什么要过来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从右边…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海你也稍微睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 也不知道迎接学姐的人什么时候会来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那为了打消睡意我告诉你一件好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前一段时间我向柑菜告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}骗人 那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然结果我早已料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以你才会把谷川的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}告诉我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啊 太过于只顾考虑自己的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我不想你也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有呢 去冲縄的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被美樱告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在想啊 上了高中之后什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚想做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就发生了好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}尤其是从学姐来了之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个夏天真了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}毕竟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可是宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然我只能做到这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是能找到就好了呢 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你的“地方”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你的“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以再睡一会儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们都已经醒了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要不干脆 我给你做膝枕？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们在卿卿我我个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找…找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没被检查过的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 能听到么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搜查队在星球附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快从…那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 快让我们跳跃到刚才找到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么会…反连环力场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(722,664)}linkage anti-field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笼罩着整个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无法传送
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么办 就算是坐电车去也要花3小时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}追兵不是要来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不快点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无人驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 柠檬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我早料到会有这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提前准备了车真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 你有驾驶证啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会派什么人来接你？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概会和之前一样是救援飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对方会通过搜索你的生物资料而来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 但为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}披上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会将你放出的生物反应减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个装置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}按下开关之后会产生和一夏的生物资料一样的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道这也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是受你姐姐帮助而得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好 就这样一口气到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在嘎吱嘎吱的响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}追兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}让我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定要到达那里啊 海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来吧来吧 快靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}BINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下次啊 不去看电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有柑菜和海 就我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}走75号线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剩下的 还有10公里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}后面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是为了学姐才这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是为了我最喜欢的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为想要我最喜欢的人保持着微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}三年之后 会让你后悔死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要幸福啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像…没有追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明摆着的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍摄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}主角一边受到敌人攻击一边向目的地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像能拍出很棒的高潮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后结尾就交给神明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这也是拍摄电影的妙趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好 开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.13,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:34.09,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:34.99,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:22.00,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}我曾一直追寻 喜欢上你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:30.19,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}若要为它饰上最合适的言语 那大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:36.88,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}当我悄然发觉时 心绪早已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:45.38,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}紧系于你 愈缠愈紧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:52.90,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&HCD6A1D&\t(2864,3156,\3c&H0090FF)}若我不曾踌躇 对你说出那句话来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:59.03,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&HDB6CEB&\t(2551,3000,\3c&H77BD3E)}你已经不哭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:03.02,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}越过流云的浮影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:05.67,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}绘出想你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:13.95,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}在弥漫着盛夏的芳香之中 无数次浮现出你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:17.64,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}是谁曾触及那轮轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:22.40,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}像夏日午后滴咚下落的雷阵雨那般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:30.33,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}点上一抹新色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们定然无法忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}同大家一起度过的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那段特别的夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}任时光流转
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们依然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.59,0:23:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}相约彼夏

